Individual




Richard S. Stoddart



Mr. Richard S. Stoddart is Independent Director at Hasbro, Inc., Chairman at The American Advertising Federation, Chief Executive Office at Leo Burnett Worldwide, Inc. and President at Arc Worldwide, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Hasbro, Inc. 
Mr. Stoddart was previously employed as Manager-Marketing Communications by Ford Motor Co. 
He received his undergraduate degree from Dartmouth College.



